Show your latest Instagram images in a widget. Images are linked to Copygram, where all your Instagram images are visible in a very nice grid.

== Description ==

Show your latest Instagram images in a widget. Images are linked to Copygram, where all your Instagram images are visible in a very nice grid.

== Installation ==

This section describes how to install the plugin and get it working.

1. Upload the folder "copygram-widget" to the "/wp-content/plugins/" directory

2. Activate the plugin through the "Plugins" menu in WordPress

3. Got to "Widgets" (under "Appearance") and add one or more "Copygram widget" from "Available Widgets"

4. Do your settings. Your "Copygram url" is http://copygr.am/ + your Instagram username

